         <div class="title"><span style="font-size:30px">Mobile Business</span></div><br><br>
<p><img src="../images/ir/monthly/op0012.png" /></p>
<p class="remark">Note :<br/>
1. The monthly of contract pre-paid card subscribers will be classified as the pre-paid subscribers from December 2000 onwards. For the ease of analysis of investors, we will implement the same practice in the future. The monthly of contract pre-paid card subscribers will not be re-stated for the period prior to December 2000. <br/><br/>
2. The weighted average annual churn rate of the 13 operating subsidiaries for the full year of 2000 were 5.4% (not including the transfer by subscribers between various brands of services of the Group) and 11.2% (including the transfer by subscribers between various brands of services of the Group).
</p>
<p><img src="../images/ir/monthly/op0011.png" /></p>
