<p><img src="../images/ir/monthly/op0007.png" /></p>
<p><img src="../images/ir/monthly/op0006.png" /></p>
<p class="remark">Note: <br/>
1. From June onwards, the prepaid subscriber monthly reflects the monthly of valid prepaid cards after activation. Prior to this, the prepaid card subscriber monthly reflects monthly of cards sold. </p>
